# ============================================================
#  Atlas — root template. The REAL env Atlas loads is apps/api/.env
#  (gitignored). Copy apps/api/.env.example -> apps/api/.env and fill
#  your keys there. Do NOT put real secrets in this tracked file.
# ============================================================
